    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka to introduce 5-year-multiple entry tourist VISA",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka's Cabinet of Ministers granted approval for a 5-year multiple entry tourist visa with a 6-month stay for 35 countries.",
        "Tourism Minister Harin Fernando tweeted that this is in addition to the 1-year multiple entry and single entry tourist visa which have a 6-month stay period, which was earlier limited 30 days.",
        "He said the new measures will help boost tourism in Sri Lanka.",
        "Tokyo will coordinate with other Sri Lanka creditors on debt"
      ],
